      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — 6 L/min 2500 RPM",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted velocity magnitude against particle image velocimetry measurements in the volute at 6 L/min, 2500 RPM. Agreement within 8% RMS across the measurement plane. Uncertainty quantification performed via Monte Carlo propagation of inlet boundary condition variability (500 samples).",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
